CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: enVVeno Medical Corp is a medical device company focused on the development of innovative bioprosthetic (tissue-based) devices to improve the standard of care in the treatment of venous disease. Its lead product, the VenoValve, is a first-in-class, surgical implant being developed for the treatment of severe deep venous Chronic Venous Insufficiency (CVI).
